Name: Vivienne
Phrase: We did what she said and really did get out of the maze.

Name: Putra
Phrase: But isn't the Mist a bit too thick? All the monsters were tough too.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: It's to be expected that there's a Phantom Mist. I won't complain, it's our job to fight in the Mist.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Yes, the Mist is getting thicker, but I think we've managed to escape the complicated maze. It's a good thing that the gradient got a lot steeper after we took that branch to the right. It's easier to get lost going up than to repeatedly go up and down, because we're less likely to get lost.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: But Yoshino and friend's goal is not to climb the mountain. Our goal is to find Miyako and get back down the mountain.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: If Miyako is aiming for the summit, we will catch up with her sooner or later; If Miyako descends the mountain first, that means she's safe, still good.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Don't worry, Yoshino. We'll catch up. We'll be quicker than her in fighting our way up the mountain. Even Miyako can't run up the mountain in this Mist without being noticed by the monsters.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: The bad magic has become stronger after we passed through the torii earlier. It could be possible that she's stuck and hiding somewhere...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: It appears that Miss Yoshino is right.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Queensway?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Miss Yakutsk, please turn around.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: I won't be falling for the same trick anymore. I'm not afraid of fox masks.
Yakutsk turned around as told by Queensway...

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: GWAAAH!
This time, it was Miyako standing right behind Yakutsk. Nobody's floating in mid-air this time as expected, but nobody noticed Miyako until Queensway spotted her.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Miyako, you're okay. So glad. Was so worried.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I was so surprised. It really was Yoshino-chan. I thought I could smell Yoshino-chan's scent, so I came out and was surprised to see you right in front of me.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: But it's not just Yoshino right~?

Name: Putra
Phrase: That's right~? So we're Yoshino's light bulbs~?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Ah, yes. I didn't smell anyone else other than Yoshino-chan, so I had no idea who else was there.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Wait, you're really treating us like light bulbs-!

Name: Miyako
Phrase: It's not that I treated you all as light bulbs. Yoshino-chan has a distinctive smell. I can clearly detect her even when I'm inside a barrier that repels all magic power.

Name: Putra
Phrase: There it is. The animal-like abilities unique to the beast girls.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: If we want to be technical it's not exactly the same thing, but it's okay to recognise it that way.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Wait a minute. You may fool the spear-using, assault-charging Putra, but you can't fool magical girl Vivienne by using such ambiguous language.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Magical girl, you...?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Oui? Problem?

Name: Putra
Phrase: No, nothing.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Erhem.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Yoshino and I were both walking around with our antennas beep-beep-ing to look for you, Miyako, okay? Then you suddenly appeared behind us. I'm noooot convinced that you sniffed her out by scent.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: That's because neither I nor any of you were able to detect each other's magic.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: You say you have a barrier that repels magic? That's easy for you to say, but we don't see that kind of thing very often, do we? If you have such an item, I'd like to know about it.

Name: Putra
Phrase: As expected of the magical gorilla. You're reliable when it comes to magic and magical powers.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Magical Girl.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Yes, sorry.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: “There's a special barrier sorcery on these torii gates here. I made good use of it to hide myself. There are a lot of demons here, so I thought I'd take a break.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Barrier sorcery...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: This is a major oversight. A little thought and this could have been figured out too...

Name: Putra
Phrase: Being able to hide in the torii gates is an amazingly convenient feature. What was the point of all that effort we put in to get here?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: You have to be able to excel in Nishiki sorcery to a certain extent. It seems that the Railway Army troops couldn't do it.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Oh, but I would have figured that Yoshino-chan can do it...

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Yoshino is in a very bad state because of the magic of these torii gates. We are asking her to conserve her magic and strength as much as possible.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: She's exhausted enough dealing with the Phantom Mist and searching for you. We didn't have time to investigate the torii.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: No, we had time for that. If only Yoshino had thought it through better...

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: You didn't think of it right away because it sounded too difficult. It's fine, it doesn't matter. We got Miyako safely this way, and there is no casualties.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: That's right, Yoshino. Don't worry about it.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Miss Miyako, my apologies for asking immediately after we met... Can you tell us why you came back here alone? There must be a reason why you were separated from the rest of the Railway Army, right? Because if there's anything left to do, we're here to help...

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Yoshino's condition is our top priority.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Yes, of course it is.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino will be fine. Let's look for the children together, shall we?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: That's up to me to decide, Yoshino-chan.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Eh? What do you mean?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yoshino-chan, you've been getting worse since you met me, haven't you?

Name: Putra
Phrase: Hey Miyako, tell me very honestly. Is Yoshino looking alright to you?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I don't think she's alright at all, no matter how I look at it. You shouldn't have brought her here.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: It's our fault. I'm so sorry. We made a mistake.
No, it is my responsibility as the commander to care for the state of my subordinates. I thought about retreating on the way out, but due to the fact that we were lost, we could only go on.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: It's alright. I can handle this. If it's pain and suffering you're feeling now, Yoshino-chan, I can absorb it. I can absorb it with my sorcery.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yoshino-chan, why don't you hold my hand? After that, let's take a short rest. If you are okay with that, let's go together.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Are you okay with that, Miyako, sucking out the pain?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I'm fine. It's my special ability.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Trust me. This is very effective for us Nishiki folk.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Understood... believe.
Yoshino quietly closed her eyes and gently held Miyako's offered hand.
Some sort of black things were sucked out of Yoshino's body. These black things then went straight through Miyako's hand into Miyako's body.

Name: Putra
Phrase: W-What was that...?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Miyako sucked something out of Yoshino. I don't know what it is...

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes, she will be fine after a short rest. Conductor-san, let's take shelter inside the torii for the time being and regain our bearings. I will deploy a repelling barrier, so please pass through the gate while I do so.
Miyako held Yoshino's body in her arms and began to chant a curse at the torii gate in front of her.
This is advanced sorcery. Very strong magical forces gathered around the torii. This sorcery would not merely at the level of "a bit difficult".

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Come on, everyone, this way.
Miyako passed between the pillars of the torii gate. Her figure and presence completely disappeared from our sight.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: I knew Miyako was no ordinary woman, but she's stronger than I imagined.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: We should have been accompanied by someone familiar with sorcery.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Miss Yakutsk?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: We should have been the ones to use our brains. Sometimes one can be affected by bad influences because they can do sorcery. This is something one can figure out with just a bit of thought...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: It's pointless for us to regret it now. We can make the most of it next time.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Yes, I know.
